title: Our Intern Recaps The City Girl Walk + Kristin's Date Night Was A Failure!
description:
Kristin made a promise to have at least one date night a month with her husband. So far, they have successfully gone on dates. But the last date didn't go as planned. 
But first, our intern Bella gives us the inside scoop on the Atlanta City Girl Walk.
